{"type":"message","id":"0a1ee409","parentId":"adfbde9d","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:09:31.010Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_01QiWjSrEUsesJkPi7f32YWp","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"exec\",\n  \"error\": \"exec denied: Cron runs cannot wait for interactive exec approval.\\nEffective host exec policy: security=allowlist ask=always askFallback=allowlist\\nStricter values from tools.exec and ~/.openclaw/exec-approvals.json both apply.\\nFix one of these:\\n- align both files to security=\\\"full\\\" and ask=\\\"off\\\" for trusted local automation\\n- keep allowlist mode and add an explicit allowlist entry for this command\\n- enable Web UI, terminal UI, or chat exec approvals and rerun interactively\\nTip: run \\\"openclaw doctor\\\" and \\\"openclaw approvals get --gateway\\\" to inspect the effective policy.\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"exec","error":"exec denied: Cron runs cannot wait for interactive exec approval.\nEffective host exec policy: security=allowlist ask=always askFallback=allowlist\nStricter values from tools.exec and ~/.openclaw/exec-approvals.json both apply.\nFix one of these:\n- align both files to security=\"full\" and ask=\"off\" for trusted local automation\n- keep allowlist mode and add an explicit allowlist entry for this command\n- enable Web UI, terminal UI, or chat exec approvals and rerun interactively\nTip: run \"openclaw doctor\" and \"openclaw approvals get --gateway\" to inspect the effective policy."},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775275771009}}
{"type":"message","id":"d2bef3b3","parentId":"0a1ee409","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:09:44.381Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The exec is blocked in cron runs due to allowlist policy. I need to inform the user that the script can't run in this cron context without proper exec approval configuration.\n\nLet me provide a report based on what I can read from files, or explain the situation clearly.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🔒 夜间安全巡检报告 — 2026-04-04\n\n**⚠️ 巡检未能执行：exec 权限策略阻止了脚本运行**\n\n---\n\n### 问题说明\n\nCron 任务在隔离环境中运行，但当前 exec 策略为 `security=allowlist`，且 cron 环境**不支持交互式审批等待**，导致脚本无法执行。\n\n**错误信息：**\n> `exec denied: allowlist miss` — Cron runs cannot wait for interactive exec approval.\n\n---\n\n### 🔧 修复方法（三选一）\n\n**方案 A（推荐）：为该脚本添加 allowlist 条目**\n```bash\nopenclaw approvals get --gateway   # 查看当前策略\n```\n在 `~/.openclaw/exec-approvals.json` 中为 `bash /home/gaoweiwei/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/nightly-security-audit.sh` 添加白名单规则。\n\n**方案 B：对可信本地自动化放开限制**\n在 exec 策略中设置 `security=full` + `ask=off`（仅限本地受信主机）。\n\n**方案 C：手动运行**\n在终端直接执行：\n```bash\nbash /home/gaoweiwei/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/nightly-security-audit.sh\n```\n\n---\n\n### 📋 建议下一步\n\n伟伟，建议运行 `openclaw doctor` 检查有效策略，然后选择上述方案之一配置 allowlist，之后 cron 就能正常跑了。需要我帮你生成 allowlist 配置内容吗？🍒"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"opencode","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":553,"cacheRead":19547,"cacheWrite":254,"totalTokens":20355,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.008295,"cacheRead":0.0058641,"cacheWrite":0.0009525,"total":0.0151146}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775275771010,"responseId":"msg_bdrk_01D83UZvR5rMG944XgAh4Shg"}}
